'''Friday Wilson''' (born '''Liz Wilson''' on [[November 29]], [[1979]]) portrayed the [[Naboo Royal Handmaidens|handmaiden]] [[Eirtaé]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']]. She was credited as "Friday 'Liz' Wilson" in the movie.

